channel.title: Server Starter File! Read!

the link = http://www.mediafire.com/?sharekey=cbfdb805734c8957b94117dade8fc295e04e75f6e8ebb871
If you have any suggestions to put something in there i will look into it.Im a little busy atm.I hope you all download it. :)
